{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":686,"text":"So what I want to try to do is tell a quick story"},{"time":3684,"text":"about a 404 page and a lesson that was learned as a result of it."},{"time":7394,"text":"But to start it probably helps to have an understanding"},{"time":10113,"text":"of what a 404 page actually is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13625,"text":"The 404 page is that."},{"time":16731,"text":"It's that broken experience on the Web."},{"time":19071,"text":"It's effectively the default page"},{"time":21382,"text":"when you ask a website for something and it can't find it."},{"time":24958,"text":"And it serves you the 404 page."},{"time":27258,"text":"It's inherently a feeling of being broken when you go through it."},{"time":32083,"text":"And I just want you to think a little bit about, remember for yourself,"},{"time":34708,"text":"it's annoying when you hit this thing."},{"time":37750,"text":"Because it's the feeling of a broken relationship."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40008,"text":"And that's where it's actually also interesting to think about,"},{"time":42750,"text":"where does 404 come from?"},{"time":44625,"text":"It's from a family of errors actually --"},{"time":46669,"text":"a whole set of relationship errors,"},{"time":48779,"text":"which, when I started digging into them,"},{"time":51083,"text":"it looks almost like a checklist\nfor a sex therapist or a couples counselor."},{"time":55917,"text":"You sort of get down there to the bottom and things get really dicey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59042,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":61931,"text":"Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63958,"text":"But these things are everywhere."},{"time":66202,"text":"They're on sites big, they're on sites small."},{"time":68898,"text":"This is a global experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71583,"text":"What a 404 page tells you"},{"time":74460,"text":"is that you fell through the cracks."},{"time":78617,"text":"And that's not a good experience"},{"time":80375,"text":"when you're used to experiences like this."},{"time":82819,"text":"You can get on your Kinect"},{"time":84092,"text":"and you can have unicorns dancing"},{"time":86250,"text":"and rainbows spraying out of your mobile phone."},{"time":88887,"text":"A 404 page is not what you're looking for."},{"time":90977,"text":"You get that, and it's like a slap in the face."},{"time":94429,"text":"Trying to think about how a 404 felt,"},{"time":96662,"text":"and it would be like if you went to Starbucks"},{"time":98542,"text":"and there's the guy behind the counter"},{"time":100292,"text":"and you're over there and there's no skim milk."},{"time":102104,"text":"And you say, \"Hey, could you bring the skim milk?\""},{"time":104083,"text":"And they walk out from behind the counter and they've got no pants on."},{"time":106248,"text":"And you're like, \"Oh, I didn't want to see that.\""},{"time":109190,"text":"That's the 404 feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111294,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112952,"text":"I mean, I've heard about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115208,"text":"So where this comes into play and why this is important"},{"time":119346,"text":"is I head up a technology incubator,"},{"time":120677,"text":"and we had eight startups sitting around there."},{"time":122677,"text":"And those startups are focused on what they are, not what they're not,"},{"time":125713,"text":"until one day Athletepath,"},{"time":127509,"text":"which is a website that focuses on services for extreme athletes,"},{"time":131187,"text":"found this video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132625,"text":"(Video) Guy: Joey!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136190,"text":"Crowd: Whoa!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":140994,"text":"Renny Gleeson: You just ... no, he's not okay."},{"time":144375,"text":"They took that video and they embedded it in their 404 page"},{"time":148418,"text":"and it was like a light bulb went off for everybody in the place."},{"time":151250,"text":"Because finally there was a page"},{"time":153958,"text":"that actually felt like what it felt like to hit a 404."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157159,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158685,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160466,"text":"So this turned into a contest."},{"time":162833,"text":"Dailypath that offers inspiration"},{"time":165083,"text":"put inspiration on their 404 page."},{"time":167579,"text":"Stayhound, which helps you find pet sitters through your social network,"},{"time":171495,"text":"commiserated with your pet."},{"time":173315,"text":"Each one of them found this."},{"time":174708,"text":"It turned into a 24-hour contest."},{"time":175958,"text":"At 4:04 the next day, we gave out $404 in cash."},{"time":179083,"text":"And what they learned"},{"time":180500,"text":"was that those little things, done right, actually matter,"},{"time":182884,"text":"and that well-designed moments can build brands."},{"time":185530,"text":"So you take a look out in the real world,"},{"time":187458,"text":"and the fun thing is you can actually hack these yourself."},{"time":189900,"text":"You can type in an URL and put in a 404 and these will pop."},{"time":192831,"text":"This is one that commiserates with you."},{"time":194829,"text":"This is one that blames you."},{"time":196579,"text":"This is one that I loved."},{"time":198417,"text":"This is an error page,"},{"time":200750,"text":"but what if this error page was also an opportunity?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":204796,"text":"So it was a moment in time"},{"time":206962,"text":"where all of these startups had to sit and think"},{"time":209233,"text":"and got really excited about what they could be."},{"time":211555,"text":"Because back to the whole relationship issue,"},{"time":214152,"text":"what they figured out through this exercise"},{"time":216409,"text":"was that a simple mistake can tell me what you're not,"},{"time":219246,"text":"or it can remind me of why I should love you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222565,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224323,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}